Chewy Pharmacy Pet Medications

Not only does Chewy offer the best pet supplies, but you can also order pet prescriptions and have them delivered right to your doorstep. There's no need to take a trip to the vet's office to pick up pet medications during office hours. Instead, you can order dog medicine and cat medicine online along with your regular cat supplies and dog supplies and receive them in your Chewy box in less than a week - before your pets run out of the veterinary medicines they need. No matter what pet prescriptions your furry friends need, you can have them filled in our online pet pharmacy. Chewy makes ordering and refilling your pet meds online an easy and quick process from start to finish. You can even add them to your Autoship account, so you'll never forget to reorder pet medications. Our dedicated Chewy Rx team will answer any questions you have, and they will even contact your veterinarian to approve online pet medications.

To handle ticks and fleas on dogs and cats, Chewy has plenty of easy-to-use flea and tick prescription medications. Once you and your veterinarian decide on the best treatment for your pets, you can order your pet Rx online to prevent itchy skin and home infestations. It's a good idea to keep these on your Autoship, because flea and tick treatment is recommended year-round. Heartworms are another pest that you'll need to protect your pup from, and you'll find plenty of options for heartworm prevention medicine for dogs in Chewy Pharmacy, along with the best in heartworm prevention medicine for cats.

Senior pets can benefit from veterinary medicines that help manage joint pain like pet arthritis medications and other pain relief prescriptions. To keep your pet's oral health on track, especially in between regular cleanings, we offer cat and dog dental care options, including prescription chews, sprays and wipes.

For the many pets who suffer from food, environmental or seasonal allergies, Chewy stocks allergy medicine for dogs and cats.

Whatever your ear and eye needs are, Chewy's online pharmacy has you covered.

Dog anxiety can be eased with special dog anxiety medication, and birds and cats can also find relief with our special calming aids. We also carry pet prescriptions for all types of animals, including veterinary medicines for dehydration, skin and coat, allergy and antibiotics for small animals, birds, reptiles and horses.

Browse Chewy Pharmacy to find the medications that your vet has prescribed. Ordering your pet meds online is simple-all you need is a current prescription. Chewy's pet Rx team will even reach out to your vet's office, and they are here to answer any questions. Add your pet prescriptions to your regular Autoship so you never have to remember to order refills. Chewy Pharmacy makes it easy and convenient to keep your pets happy and healthy.

Frequently Asked Questions about Chewy Pharmacy Pet Medications

Where do you fill pet prescriptions?

Fill pet prescriptions through a trusted pet pharmacy. There are many great pet pharmacy options, both online and in bricks-and-mortar locations, so you should have no trouble filling prescriptions for your pets. Some local pharmacies will fill pet prescriptions if they are for medicines they carry, and your vet may be able to fill prescriptions for pet medications, as well. The Chewy Pharmacy has a great selection of pet prescription medications and will deliver them to you.

Are online pet pharmacies safe?

Online pet pharmacies are safe as long as you do business with a reputable company. Choose a pet pharmacy with a known reputation for safety and quality, like the Chewy Pharmacy, and check out online reviews or ask your vet if you are unsure. Beware of any pet pharmacy that does not require a prescription and know that overseas companies are not subject to the same safety regulations as US pet pharmacies.

How do you get a pet prescription online?

Get a pet prescription online through a reputable pet pharmacy, like the Chewy Pharmacy, after visiting your vet for an exam. When you order from the Chewy Pharmacy, you can order the medications your vet prescribes by simply selecting the product(s) and providing your vets infowe will then contact your veterinarian to verify the prescription. Other online pharmacies may be able to contact your vet, or they may have you upload a written or electronic prescription instead.
